'''2017年羅馬尼亞反貪污示威'''為[[索林·葛林多努|索林·葛林多努]]宣誓就職[[羅馬尼亞|羅馬尼亞]]總理後，{{tsl|en|Ministry of Justice (Romania)|司法部 (羅馬尼亞)|司法部}}提出赦免部分犯罪及修改{{tsl|en|Penal Code of Romania|羅馬尼亞刑法}}（主要涉及濫權部分）後，所引發的大規模示威<ref name="auto">{{cite web |url=http://www.politico.eu/article/romanians-protest-government-plan-to-commute-sentences/ |title=Romanians protest government plan to commute sentences |work=Politico |author=Carmen Paun |date=22 January 2017 |accessdate=2017-02-08 |archive-date=2020-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815171823/https://www.politico.eu/article/romanians-protest-government-plan-to-commute-sentences/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

儘管受到現任[[國家自由黨|國家自由黨]][[羅馬尼亞總統|羅馬尼亞總統]][[克勞斯·約翰尼斯|克勞斯·約翰尼斯]]、司法部門及公眾的反對，新任[[社會民主黨|社會民主黨]]政府仍秘密地<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.hotnews.ro/stiri-top_news-21570944-romanian-government-secretly-adopts-emergency-ordinances-critics-say-undermine-fight-against-corruption.htm|title=Romanian government secretly adopts emergency ordinances critics say undermine fight against corruption|work=HotNews.ro|author=de Costin Ionescu|date=31 January 2017|accessdate=2017-02-08|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122194955/http://english.hotnews.ro/stiri-top_news-21570944-romanian-government-secretly-adopts-emergency-ordinances-critics-say-undermine-fight-against-corruption.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>於2017年1月31日通過羅馬尼亞刑法及刑事訴訟法的修正案<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.politico.eu/article/romanians-protest-government-plan-to-commute-sentences/ |title=Romanians protest government plan to commute sentences |work=[[Politico|Politico]] |author=Carmen Paun |date=22 January 2017 |accessdate=2017-02-08 |archive-date=2020-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815171823/https://www.politico.eu/article/romanians-protest-government-plan-to-commute-sentences/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。反對者認為該修正案將合法化政府貪汙，並使數百名現任或前任政治人物免于刑事調查及處罰<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-esential-21569643-nucleara-din-justitie-lista-potentialilor-beneficiari-dezincrimarii-mascate-abuzului-serviciu.htm?nomobile=|title=Nucleara din justitie. Lista potentialilor beneficiari ai dezincriminarii mascate a abuzului in serviciu|newspaper=HotNewsRo|language=ro|access-date=2017-02-02|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121231159/http://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-esential-21569643-nucleara-din-justitie-lista-potentialilor-beneficiari-dezincrimarii-mascate-abuzului-serviciu.htm?nomobile=|dead-url=no}}</ref>，於修正案通過當晚，即有超過25,000民眾參與示威，隔日全國則有超過30萬人參與示威，是為[[1989年羅馬尼亞革命|1989年羅馬尼亞革命]]以來羅馬尼亞最大規模的示威<ref name=Digi241Feb>{{cite web |url=http://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/evenimente/protest-1-februarie-guvern-adoptare-oug-coduri-penale-660631 |title=Cel mai amplu protest din ultimii 25 de ani. Peste 300.000 de oameni au fost în stradă |work=Digi24 |author=[[Digi24|Digi24]] |date=1 February 2017 |accessdate=2017-02-08 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111233440/http://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/evenimente/protest-1-februarie-guvern-adoptare-oug-coduri-penale-660631 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，抗議群眾數量於2月5日達到高峰，據[[Digi_24|Digi 24]]估計全國示威人數達60萬人<ref name=Digi245Feb>{{cite web |url=http://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/justitie/legea-gratierii/cel-mai-mare-protest-fata-de-oug-13-anuntat-pentru-duminica-in-capitala-663703 |title=#Ro-mânia, ziua a şasea: 600.000 de oameni în stradă, din care 300.000 la Guvern |work=Digi24 |author=[[Digi24|Digi24]] |date=5 February 2017 |accessdate=2017-02-08 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013340/https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/justitie/legea-gratierii/cel-mai-mare-protest-fata-de-oug-13-anuntat-pentru-duminica-in-capitala-663703 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

